{"tid":527192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《明報》聲明：會員專區混淆國家、地區選項　已修正並表致歉","createTime":"2018-01-12T11:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T12:38:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba937b96bd3fb101b61102b929bf56efdb0bb8e4","tid":527192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"《明報》發表聲明：本報會員服務專區的網上表格，在「資訊電郵服務登記」的「聯絡資料」一欄中，由於取用坊間預設程式，只設有「國家」一項，混淆了國家和地區選項，現已修正為「國家／地區」。現向讀者和各界致歉，疏忽之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00001/1515755346389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00001%2F1515755346389&d=e6t5oc2tazXYM9yn%2BQzmf9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ef3ee4c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00001%2F1515755346389&h=8f25c46c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00001/1515755346389</a>"},{"pid":"7b471355f8e2d3bc012668c8cdd936facb35a995","tid":527192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"開始自我審查"},{"pid":"f6a932014cffca5462acd2252d63e4eb9e310f7e","tid":527192,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"明報不明"},{"pid":"bbd0711bce369e4fb4f658cd5ad0c41cab674fe0","tid":527192,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b471355f8e2d3bc012668c8cdd936facb35a995","tid":527192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"開始自我審查"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"&gt; 開始? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690120a3cf4fa9dfc9bae2f0bdf9004f51f085b2","tid":527192,"uid":39464